title: Blacksnake Moan
description:
A God-fearing bluesman (Jackson) takes to a wild young woman (Ricci) who, as a victim of childhood sexual abuse, looks everywhere for love, never quite finding it.
-imdb.com

One of my favorite movies, strong performances from all involved, most surprisingly of all Justin Timberlake.  Samuel L. Jackson\\\&#039;s a decent singer to boot and only adds to his badassity with some firery blues numbers.
